    <li><a href="/llmrouter/docs/providers/openai">OpenAI provider</a> — default embedding backend.</li>
    <li><a href="/llmrouter/docs/concepts/byte-passthrough">Byte passthrough</a> — the same Raw pattern as chat.</li>
  </ul>
</DocsLayout>
